/*------------------------------------------------------------------
 MBlue Nav-Style Statusbar Vista (Ver. 0.4.6)

Author: M.BLUE - Tested on: Firefox 3.5.2 - Last Update: 22.09.2009
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
1. Combine Statusbar + Findbar + Download-Statusbar in one line!
2. Gives the Statusbar the Nav-Buttons style (Vista).
3. Gives the Findbar the Nav-Buttons style (Vista).
4. Gives the Download-Statusbar the Nav-Buttons style (Vista).
5. Supports a lot of extensions.
6. Transforms "GlaZoom", "YASS", "Clear-Fields", "Find in Numbers".
7. Create a Dynamic Icon that changes aspect based on state and
   when hovering different type of links (*).
8. Highly customizable.
9. Integrates with the other Nav-Style styles.

Notes:
-Using other Styles/Extensions/Themes may interfere with the
 Statusbar/Findbar/Download-Statusbar margins/settings.
 If so, try not using other styles that changes margins/settings
 in the Statusbar/Findbar, and use the default firefox theme.
 Try keeping the statusbar clean.

-Some extensions may place some icons/buttons on the Statusbar
 left side, just before the Statusbar text. You should change
 the position ot these elements to the right side of the bar, or
 place them in another toolbar. Also it's suggested to have the
 bar as clean as possible, to give the Findbar/Download-Statusbar
 more space when opened.

-This style is optimized for using with high screen resolutions,
 a width of at least 1280px is recommended if you want to use the
 Download-Statusbar Extension. Or you can adjust the width in the
 customize section.

-You may need to edit some values under the STATUSBAR DYNAMIC ICON
 section if using a different language (*).
--------------------------------------------------------------------
CUSTOMIZING:

 1. FINDBAR WIDTH.
 2. DOWNLOAD-STATUSBAR WIDTH.
 3. FINDBAR TEXTBOX WIDTH.
 4. DOWNLOAD-STATUSBAR ITEMS WIDTH.
 5. STATUSBAR BACKGROUND COLOR.
 6. FINDBAR/DOWNLOAD-STATUSBAR BACKGROUND COLOR.
 7. STATUSBAR EXTENSIONS TEXT SIZE/WEIGHT/COLOR. 
 8. STATUSBAR TEXT SIZE/WEIGHT/COLOR/ALIGN.
 9. FINDBAR TEXT WEIGHT/COLOR.
10. DOWNLOAD-STATUSBAR TEXT SIZE/WEIGHT/COLOR/ALIGN.
11. DOWNLOAD ICONS OPACITY.
12. ITEMS OPACITY.
13. PROGRESS-BAR SETTINGS.

> GO TO BOTTOM OF THE PAGE TO CUSTOMIZE
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Supported Extensions:
 Clear Fields, Find in Numbers, ForecastFox, FoxClocks, Glazoom, 
 Yet Another Smooth Scrolling (YASS), Download-Statusbar,
 Extended Statusbar(CLASSIC STYLE ONLY), NoScript.

Integrates with:
 MBlue Combine Nav-Buttons Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Url-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Buttons Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Tabs Vista
>MBlue Nav-Style Statusbar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Throbber Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Bookmarks-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Awesome-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Menubar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Popup Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista (Downloads, Addons, Extensions)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Updates:
22.09.2009 ver. 0.4.6 = added NoScript support
20.08.2009 ver. 0.4.5 = few fixes
14.05.2009 Ver. 0.4.4 = few fixes
08.05.2009 Ver. 0.4.3 = added support for GlaZoom new version again
04.03.2009 Ver. 0.4.1 = added support for GlaZoom new version
08.02.2009 Ver. 0.4.0 = added "Extended Statusbar" support
...
16.09.2008 Ver. 0.3.0 = lot of changes and fixes
...
12.08.2008 Ver. 0.2.0 = code optimized, ready to release
...
07.08.2008 Ver. 0.1.0 = temp version
------------------------------------------------------------------*/



